  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK190">
<l>ētilār kuṟṟampōṟ ṟamkuṟṟaṅ kāṇkiṟpiṟ</l>
<l>ṟītuṇṭō maṉṉu muyirkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If they observed their own faults as they observe the faults of others, would any evil happen to men ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
